{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780929275830,"sessionID":"ses_15858491bffeXJMuegc5mX6JyJ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_6y7CUU0ahY31wIYU4nVwnzDJ","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a senior memory-systems research analyst performing READ-ONLY analysis. Do NOT write, create, edit, or delete any files. Final answer text is deliverable. Iteration 014: Indexing & freshness for authored-doc corpus. Study OpenLTM vendored at specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/external/OpenLtm-main/. Focus on FTS5 triggers, embeddings fingerprints, change detection, compare to system-spec-kit memory_index_scan / memory_embedding_reconcile. Classify teachings as TRANSFERS, DOC-ANALOG, ROW-COUPLED.","specFolder":"specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement","tenantId":"default","userId":"default","agentId":"opencode","limit":5,"session_id":"iteration-014-readonly","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":false},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"iteration-014-readonly\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"iteration-014-readonly\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"iteration-014-readonly\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 214,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":178